summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1940, for the improvement of North Sixty-seventh Street, in the City of Seattle, from Woodlawn Avenue to East Green Lake Boulevard, by grading and curbing the same, and constructing concrete sidewalks thereon, under Ordinance No. 20058, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
